Rating: 3
I used this recipe as a base to sort of build my own. I didn't use any chilis and subbed stale corn bread and white dinner rolls, cubed. I also diced up some orange and red bell peppers. This went great with my Mexican-themed Thanksgiving but is definitely something I would make again.

