Rating: 3
This is a great, tasty recipe. Very colorful, too. Excellent flavor. I don't think I changed a thing. Served it with turkey to guests who had never had cornbread stuffing in their lives. Ate ever drop. The regular buttermilk cornbread recipe is one of the best I've made.

